text:
Jumanji is perfectly awesome; genuinely enjoyed it. I find this movie very entertaining, because:1) It's relevant to me as a young person as if I've been thru (most of) what's happening on the screen myself;
2) The characters are genuine and you empathize them pretty much all the time;
3) There are some useful and teaching stuff throughout the title, which is a big plus to the plot;
3) Personally, I love Karen Gillan's character and herself, she's so enchanting and pretty and sexy;
4) It is all about fun and laughter; you are never going to get bored watching Jumanji!With that said, I wholeheartedly and sincerely adored Jumanji and thus, give it a 9. Jumanji is a decent way to spend your time, especially when it comes to your family and the one(s) you love.
